* Health: Take a 20-minute walk daily, practice yoga twice a week, or drink 8 glasses of water every day. 

* Personal Growth: Read one book, start a gratitude journal, or limit screen time to one hour before bed. 


* Financial: Create a weekly budget, limit dining out to once a week, or save a specific percentage of income. 

* Productivity/Career: Clean up the email inbox daily, update the resume, or take on a new, small responsibility at work. 
